{"word":"σχεδίην","slug":"σχεδίην","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>σχεδίην</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:accusative'>acc.</a> <a href='S:feminine'>fem.</a> of <a href='S:σχέδιος'><el>σχέδιος</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b>of Place, <i>near, close at hand</i>, <a href='S:Latin'>Lat.</a> <el>cominus</el>, <b><a href='S:Iliad'>Il.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b>of Time, <i>straightway, at once</i>, <b><a href='S:Babrius'>Babr.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}